<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top=
: 30px; margin-bottom: 0;">Everything is seating charts</h2><p style=3D"mar=
gin: 16px 0;">I could not possibly have enjoyed <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24145865.258020/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnL=
mNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDYtMTQvYmFyZWx5LWhpcmVkLWF0LW1vcmdhbi1zdGFu=
bGV5LXRyYWRpbmctc2F2aW9yLW5lYXJzLWNlby1zLXBlcmNo/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB4=
7137e3d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #00=
0000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bo=
ttom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> =
this Bloomberg profile</a> of Morgan Stanley co-president Ted Pick more. It=
 is hard to pick a favorite bit=C2=A0but I suppose I have to go with this o=
ne, from Pick=E2=80=99s time as head of equities:</p><blockquote><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Along the way, he gained notoriety for a unique style =
of leadership. After getting worked up about the size of another executive=
=E2=80=99s office, feeling it was too big for his position, Pick called in =
a construction crew over the weekend and had the walls moved to shrink the =
room.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">All investment-bank mana=
gement should work like that. All the walls should be on sliding tracks, an=
